Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这 舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔洛克舰团长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔刚蒂亚需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对我过于沉重…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优秀起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到能挺起胸膛向你父亲做出交待为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团长！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团长…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确认地球的位置坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已根据银河同盟的标准坐标确定当前位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够归队了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归需要借助超光速飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 仅凭本机无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救信号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机紧急迫降到地球后发出的最初信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达银河同盟大约需要6582年16小时20分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结论 回归大部队事实上不具备可操作性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了…
